description: HUGE One bed PLUS ADD'L 2nd BEDRM or DEN/OFFICE. Stunning South Boston Luxury. Priced to sell at $785 PSF!. Central A/C. Custom Closets. Stunning Bamboo floors. Private patio rooftop deck. Located  heart of South Boston,  walking distance to trendy restaurants, shops, and recreational amenities.
